{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4673e6a37e","title":"关于游泳的几次指示","origin":"","is_range_date":true,"dates":[{"id":"8c2dcf8853","index":1,"year":1958,"month":1966,"day":7,"articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"9a72fb8ae9","index":0,"year":1958,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"4673e6a37e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji40","name":"毛泽东全集第40卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/40-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji40":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3146d36b11","type":"title","text":"关于游泳的几次指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"c6fd2123cf","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五八年九月十二日游泳后对运动员谈话","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"72013a8de6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：全国要有三亿人学会游泳，行不行呀？","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"2f94487575","type":"paragraph","text":"答：除了七岁以下，六十岁以上的人都可以学，三亿人是可以的！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"1224d84a3a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：可以，完全可以。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"02d2b8fed6","type":"paragraph","text":"（一一问过运动员的学历情况，毛泽东知道他们都是读过专科的，有相当的知识后）","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"49951f0f53","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：你们是学出来的，可是要好好工作呵！你们是年轻人哪！是吗？时间是你们的！还要向群众去学习","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"56e10f5403","type":"paragraph","text":"二","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"e11339c99c","type":"paragraph","text":"你们不要老在游泳池里面练，游泳池小。游来游去就那么一点，要多到江河里去练习","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"2c0280b23d","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"c16f637b94","type":"paragraph","text":"长江，别人都说很大，其实，大并不可怕。你们不让我游，我现在不是已经游过来了吗！美帝国主义不是很大吗？我们顶了他一下，也没有啥。所以世界上有些大的东西，其实并不可怕。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"ac855ea69f","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"f70fd249a3","type":"paragraph","text":"游泳是一项很好的运动，应该提倡。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"1fa84d0f05","type":"subtitle","text":"五","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"6cfc764da9","type":"paragraph","text":"游泳是同大自然作斗争的一种运动，你们应该到大江大海去锻炼。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"95932ef980","type":"paragraph","text":"会休息，才能持久","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"2a3277d3da","type":"paragraph","text":"时代不同了，男女都一样。男同志能办到的事情，女同志也能办得到。","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"1c0ed45333","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛泽东轻快自如地领头游着，并风趣地问一位同志","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"13cc8d4bdc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：你说是人怕水，还是水怕人？","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"217d2f1ce4","type":"paragraph","text":"答：人怕水？","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"de49896465","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：我看是水怕人。水怕人压追他。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"306ef0a023","type":"subtitle","text":"六","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"d3dc9d6b4e","type":"paragraph","text":"在江河游泳，有逆流，可以锻炼意志和勇敢。","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"},{"id":"42d47ca43f","type":"paragraph","text":"全国的江河这样多，能不能都利用起来游泳呢？全国六亿人口，能不能有三亿人口都来游泳呢","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e"}],"page":{"id":"1c0166cdf1","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"4673e6a37e","start":271,"end":272}}}},"__N_SSG":true}